domain:
(define (domain diarcdomaindomain)
(:requirements :strips :typing :fluents :negative-preconditions :equality)

(:types
	oak_log - log
	coord distance action property - concept
	interactable unlocked - property
	actor physobj - physical
	thief self trader pogoist - actor
	open_door diamond_ore key crafting_table log block_of_diamond stick safe tree_tap placeable block_of_titanium door pogo_stick wall block_of_platinum plank air breakable rubber diamond iron_pickaxe chest oak_log sapling - physobj
	crafting_table log plank sapling tree_tap - placeable
	tree_tap plank block_of_platinum log diamond_ore crafting_table - breakable
	oak_plank - plank
	concept physical - object
)

(:constants

)

(:predicates

)

(:functions
	(container ?v0 - physical ?v1 - object)
	(world ?v0 - object)
	(inventory ?v0 - actor ?v1 - object)
)

(:action craft_plank
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?log - log)

	:precondition
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?log) 1)

	:effect (and
		(increase (inventory ?actor oak_plank) 4)
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?log) 1)
	)
)
(:action get_sapling
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?facing_obj - physical ?facing_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(= (world oak_log) 0)
		(= (inventory ?actor sapling) 0)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?facing_obj ?facing_dist)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?facing_obj ?facing_dist))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase (inventory ?actor sapling) 1)
	)
)
(:action trade_0
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?block_of_platinum - block_of_platinum)

	:precondition (and
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?block_of_platinum) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor trader_103 two)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?block_of_platinum) 1)
		(increase (inventory ?actor block_of_titanium) 1)
	)
)
(:action place_sapling
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?sapling - sapling)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?sapling) 1)
		(holding ?actor air)
	)
	:effect (and
		(increase (world oak_log) 1)
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?sapling) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor air one))
		(facing_obj ?actor oak_log one)
	)
)
(:action break_and_pickup_tree_tap
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(not(= tree_tap diamond_ore))
		(not(= tree_tap block_of_platinum))
		(facing_obj ?actor tree_tap one)
		(not(floating tree_tap))
		(not(= tree_tap oak_log))
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (world ?obj) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase (inventory ?actor ?obj) 1)
	)
)
(:action break_and_pickup_crafting_table
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(not(= crafting_table diamond_ore))
		(not(= crafting_table block_of_platinum))
		(facing_obj ?actor crafting_table one)
		(not(floating crafting_table))
		(not(= crafting_table oak_log))
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (world ?obj) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase (inventory ?actor ?obj) 1)
	)
)
(:action break_and_pickup_diamond_ore
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(not(= diamond_ore diamond_ore))
		(not(= diamond_ore block_of_platinum))
		(facing_obj ?actor diamond_ore one)
		(not(floating diamond_ore))
		(not(= diamond_ore oak_log))
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (world ?obj) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase (inventory ?actor ?obj) 1)
	)
)
(:action break_and_pickup_oak_log
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(not(= oak_log diamond_ore))
		(not(= oak_log block_of_platinum))
		(facing_obj ?actor oak_log one)
		(not(floating oak_log))
		(not(= oak_log oak_log))
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (world ?obj) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase (inventory ?actor ?obj) 1)
	)
)
(:action break_and_pickup_oak_plank
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(not(= oak_plank diamond_ore))
		(not(= oak_plank block_of_platinum))
		(facing_obj ?actor oak_plank one)
		(not(floating oak_plank))
		(not(= oak_plank oak_log))
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (world ?obj) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase (inventory ?actor ?obj) 1)
	)
)
(:action break_and_pickup_block_of_platinum
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition (and
		(not(= block_of_platinum diamond_ore))
		(not(= block_of_platinum block_of_platinum))
		(facing_obj ?actor block_of_platinum one)
		(not(floating block_of_platinum))
		(not(= block_of_platinum oak_log))
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (world ?obj) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase (inventory ?actor ?obj) 1)
	)
)
(:action pickup
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?obj - physobj)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one)
		(floating ?obj)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (world ?obj) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase (inventory ?actor ?obj) 1)
	)
)
(:action break_and_pickup_diamond_ore
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?obj - diamond_ore)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one)
		(not(floating ?obj))
		(holding ?actor iron_pickaxe)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (world ?obj) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase (inventory ?actor diamond) 9)
	)
)
(:action craft_stick
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?plank - plank)

	:precondition
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?plank) 2)

	:effect (and
		(increase (inventory ?actor stick) 4)
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?plank) 2)
	)
)
(:action open_door
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?door - door)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor ?door one)
		(holding ?actor air)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (world ?door) 1)
		(increase (world open_door) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?door one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
	)
)
(:action collect_from_chest
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?chest - chest)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor ?chest one)
		(holding ?actor air)
		(= (container chest key) 1)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (container ?chest key) 1)
		(increase (inventory ?actor key) 1)
		(not(holding ?actor air))
		(holding ?actor key)
	)
)
(:action craft_tree_tap
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?plank - plank ?stick - stick)

	:precondition (and
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?plank) 5)
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?stick) 1)
		(facing_obj ?actor crafting_table one)
	)
	:effect (and
		(increase (inventory ?actor tree_tap) 1)
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?plank) 5)
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?stick) 1)
	)
)
(:action trade_1
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?diamond - diamond)

	:precondition (and
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?diamond) 18)
		(facing_obj ?actor trader_103 two)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?diamond) 18)
		(increase (inventory ?actor block_of_platinum) 1)
	)
)
(:action collect_from_tree_tap
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?tree_tap - tree_tap ?log - log)

	:precondition (and
		(next_to ?tree_tap ?log)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?tree_tap one)
	)
	:effect
		(increase (inventory ?actor rubber) 1)

)
(:action find_safe
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?facing_obj - physical ?facing_dist - distance)

	:precondition (and
		(= ?actor self)
		(= (world safe) 0)
		(facing_obj ?actor ?facing_obj ?facing_dist)
		(holding ?actor air)
		(>= (inventory ?actor key) 1)
	)
	:effect (and
		(increase (world safe) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?facing_obj ?facing_dist))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(holding ?actor air)
	)
)
(:action trade_3
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?log - log)

	:precondition (and
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?log) 10)
		(facing_obj ?actor trader_104 two)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?log) 10)
		(increase (inventory ?actor block_of_titanium) 1)
	)
)
(:action place_tree_tap
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?tree_tap - tree_tap ?log - log)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor ?log two)
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?tree_tap) 1)
		(holding ?actor air)
	)
	:effect (and
		(increase (world ?tree_tap) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?log two))
		(facing_obj ?actor ?tree_tap one)
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?tree_tap) 1)
		(next_to ?tree_tap ?log)
	)
)
(:action craft_block_of_diamond
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?diamond - diamond)

	:precondition (and
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?diamond) 9)
		(facing_obj ?actor crafting_table one)
	)
	:effect (and
		(increase (inventory ?actor block_of_diamond) 1)
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?diamond) 9)
	)
)
(:action collect_from_safe
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?safe - safe)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor ?safe one)
		(propertyOf ?safe unlocked)
		(= (container ?safe diamond) 18)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (container ?safe diamond) 18)
		(increase (inventory ?actor diamond) 18)
	)
)
(:action use_safe
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?safe - safe)

	:precondition (and
		(facing_obj ?actor ?safe one)
		(holding ?actor key)
	)
	:effect
		(propertyOf ?safe unlocked)

)
(:action trade_2
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?block_of_platinum - block_of_platinum)

	:precondition (and
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?block_of_platinum) 2)
		(facing_obj ?actor trader_104 two)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?block_of_platinum) 2)
		(increase (inventory ?actor diamond) 9)
	)
)
(:action break_and_pickup_block_of_platinum
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?obj - block_of_platinum)

	:precondition (and
		(not(floating ?obj))
		(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one)
		(holding ?actor iron_pickaxe)
	)
	:effect (and
		(decrease (world ?obj) 1)
		(not(facing_obj ?actor ?obj one))
		(facing_obj ?actor air one)
		(increase (inventory ?actor ?obj) 1)
	)
)
(:action craft_pogo_stick
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?stick - stick ?rubber - rubber ?block_of_titanium - block_of_titanium ?block_of_diamond - block_of_diamond)

	:precondition (and
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?stick) 2)
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?rubber) 1)
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?block_of_titanium) 2)
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?block_of_diamond) 2)
		(facing_obj ?actor crafting_table one)
	)
	:effect (and
		(increase (inventory ?actor pogo_stick) 1)
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?stick) 2)
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?rubber) 1)
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?block_of_titanium) 2)
		(decrease (inventory ?actor ?block_of_diamond) 2)
	)
)
(:action deselect
	:parameters (?actor - actor ?obj - physobj)

	:precondition (and
		(>= (inventory ?actor ?obj) 1)
		(holding ?actor ?obj)
	)
	:effect (and
		(not(holding ?actor ?obj))
		(holding ?actor air)
	)
)
(:action interact_with_pogoist_102
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition
		(facing_obj ?actor pogoist_102 two)

	:effect
		(facing_obj ?actor pogoist_102 two)

)
(:action interact_with_trader_103
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition
		(facing_obj ?actor trader_103 two)

	:effect
		(facing_obj ?actor trader_103 two)

)
(:action interact_with_trader_104
	:parameters (?actor - actor)

	:precondition
		(facing_obj ?actor trader_104 two)

	:effect
		(facing_obj ?actor trader_104 two)

)
)
